-- OMV Hires Natural Power's Turkish Unit to Consult on Wind Farm Projects
-- B y   M a r k   B e n t l e y
-- 2010-12-20T09:11:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-20/omv-hires-natural-power-s-turkish-unit-to-consult-on-wind-farm-projects.html
OMV AG , central Europe’s biggest oil
company, hired  Natural Power ’s Turkish unit to perform due
diligence, measurements and layout designs for wind energy
projects in the country.  The contract was signed after almost two years of co-
operation between the companies, Christian Johannes, chief
executive of Natural Power’s Ankara-based unit  re-consult , said
in an e-mailed statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
